Sphinx

The following commands were used to create the docs

conda install -c conda-forge sphinx sphinx-rtd-theme sphinx-copybutton
pip install sphinx-reload
sphinx-quickstart docs

Build the docs using

# Traditional
cd docs
make html

# Live reload
sphinx-reload docs
